"title": "9115: antichrist, the",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "9115",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>One who is directly and implacably opposed to Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>The antichrist will deny fundamental truths about Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7\">2JN 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22\">MRK 13:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:29\">MRK 3:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:22\">1JN 2:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:3\">1JN 4:3</a></p>\n<h2>Th antichrist as a self-appointed rival to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:3-2Thess2:4\">2TH 2:3–2:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:7-Dan7:8\">DAN 7:7–7:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:24-Dan7:25\">DAN 7:24–7:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:9-Dan8:12\">DAN 8:9–8:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:23-Dan8:25\">DAN 8:23–8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:36-Dan11:45\">DAN 11:36–11:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:1-Rev13:10\">REV 13:1–13:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:11-Rev13:18\">REV 13:11–13:18</a></p>\n<h2>The coming of the antichrist is a sign of the ``last days''</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:18\">1JN 2:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:6-2Thess2:10\">2TH 2:6–2:10</a></p>\n<h2>The final defeat of the antichrist is assured</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:8\">2TH 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan7:26-Dan7:27\">DAN 7:26–7:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan8:25\">DAN 8:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan11:45\">DAN 11:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev17:7-Rev17:14\">REV 17:7–17:14</a></p>",
